Quickstrike:





Quickstrike walked on, trying to home in on Stingtra's location. He had to 
get her talking before she did something stupid to herself.

He said to her through his comm-link, "Because yer doin' slag t' yerself an' 
yer startin' t' scare me. If boss-bot finds out 'bout this he might slag me. 
An' ya know why? Ah'm second in command! Ah don't know if ya know th' 
responsiblity in that. Ah'm still learnin'! Now where are ya?"

He looked around the area.
